                  collection on the log, thus optimising disk space usage.
                  Its claimed advantage over traditional loggers is most
                  marked in a situation where there are a few long
                  transactions amongst many short ones. This paper describes
                  the formal specification of a transactional logger based on
                  the EL algorithm, its modelling using Object-oriented
                  design(OMT) and implementation. The application of the EL
                  logger to new, emerging applications is also considered. At
